	Gerben Wierda\
	Gerben_Wierda@rna.nl\
		\
		TeXShop depends on Unix command line programs to do\
		all of the hard work; Gerben maintaines these programs. His\
		distribution is used by many TeX projects, including TeXShop,\
		iMacTeX, CMacTex, fink, and others. So he is a member of many\
		teams.\
\
		TeXShop depends on the script altpdftex by Wierda to typeset\
		using latex + ghostscript; his version of the eps2pdf script \
		handles Macintosh line feed conventions as well as Unix line\
		feed conventions. Many features of TeXShop depend on\
		contributions of Wierda to the teTeX system. \
\
	Dirk Olmes\
	dirk@xanthippe.ping.de\
\
		Broke out the code into the current series of multiple source\
		files. Dirk completely rewrote the preferences system to use\
		the Mac OS X defaults database. This rewrite has been \
		enormously valuable as additional preference options were\
		added later.\
\
