	\cb2 mitsu\cb1 @kusm.kyoto-u.ac.jp\
\
		Wrote the code for magnification in the pdf window. Wrote all\
		code for the Macro menu and Macro Editor. Modified the\
		typesetting menu and toolbar buttons so they behave in a\
		better manner. Fixed many bugs. Revised the code to offer\
		better support for users in Japan. Shishikura's contributions\
		have been crucial for version 1.27 and beyond.\
