		in the pdf output. Later D'Ancona was joined by J\'8er\'99me Laurens and\
		the two of them polished pdfsync.sty. Laurens implemented\
		pdfsync behavior in iTeXMac, the first front end implementation\
		for Mac OS X.\
\
	Sean Luke\
\
		Suggested adding an option to typeset using latex + ghostscript\
		in addition to the original pdflatex. Luke provided the first script to\
		do this. That led to Gerben Wierda's current script. I consider this\
		script one of the most import changes in TeXShop since the start\
		of the project.\
